basics.summary: Seeking a position with warehouse company, where can use experience as Forklift Driver to maintain inventories in good, clean environment. More than ten years experience. Skilled at operating in various types of weather and adept at operating hand and power tools. Able to follow safety procedures and effectively interrelate with other department workers.
